texts.label: paragraph
texts.orig: Need a username and password from the Plesk DB? Use this one-liner:
texts.text: Need a username and password from the Plesk DB? Use this one-liner:

texts.label: code
texts.orig: select REPLACE(sys_users.home,'/home/httpd/vhosts/','') AS domain,sys_users.login,accounts.password from sys_users LEFT JOIN accounts on sys_users.account_id=accounts.id;
texts.text: select REPLACE(sys_users.home,'/home/httpd/vhosts/','') AS domain,sys_users.login,accounts.password from sys_users LEFT JOIN accounts on sys_users.account_id=accounts.id;
